(8, 'Khu biệt thự Đại Phú Gia – Quy Nhơn\r\n', 'Công trình: Khu biệt thự Đại Phú Gia – Quy Nhơn[...]', '1-1.png', '<div class=\"entry-image relative\">\r\n	   <a href=\"https://dragonstone.vn/cong-trinh/khu-biet-thu-dai-phu-gia-quy-nhon/\">\r\n    <img width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://dragonstone.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/1-1.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://dragonstone.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/1-1.png 1000w, https://dragonstone.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/1-1-800x400.png 800w, https://dragonstone.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/1-1-768x384.png 768w, https://dragonstone.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/1-1-600x300.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"></a>\r\n	   <div class=\"badge absolute top post-date badge-outline\">\r\n	<div class=\"badge-inner\">\r\n		<span class=\"post-date-day\">25</span><br>\r\n		<span class=\"post-date-month is-small\">Th5</span>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>	</div>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content single-page\">\r\n\r\n	<p>Công trình: Khu biệt thự Đại Phú Gia – Quy Nhơn</p>\r\n<p>Địa chỉ:&nbsp;Trần Hưng Đạo, Phường Lê Lợi, Thành Phố Quy Nhơn, Tỉnh Bình Định</p>\r\n<p>Sản phẩm cung cấp thi công:</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 30.7637%; text-align: center; height: 21px;\"><strong>Vị trí</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 26.7291%; text-align: center; height: 21px;\"><strong>Hạng mục</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 42.5072%; text-align: center; height: 21px;\"><strong>Loại đá</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 42px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 30.7637%; height: 42px; text-align: left;\">Phòng khách</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 26.7291%; height: 42px; text-align: left; padding-left: 30px;\">Ốp tường, lát nền</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 42.5072%; height: 42px; text-align: left;\">Marble Crema Nova, đá chẻ</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 30.7637%; height: 42px; text-align: left;\" rowspan=\"2\">Phòng tắm</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 26.7291%; height: 21px; text-align: left; padding-left: 30px;\">Ốp tường, bàn lavabo</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 42.5072%; height: 21px; text-align: left;\">Marble Volakas</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 26.7291%; height: 21px; text-align: left; padding-left: 30px;\">Lát nền</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 42.5072%; height: 21px; text-align: left;\">Marble Crema Marfill kết hợp điểm đá hoa cương kim sa trung màu đen</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"slider-wrapper relative \" id=\"slider-162199000\">\r\n    <div class=\"slider slider-nav-circle slider-nav-large slider-nav-light slider-style-normal flickity-enabled is-draggable\" data-flickity-options=\"{\r\n            &quot;cellAlign&quot;: &quot;center&quot;,\r\n            &quot;imagesLoaded&quot;: true,\r\n            &quot;lazyLoad&quot;: 1,\r\n            &quot;freeScroll&quot;: false,\r\n            &quot;wrapAround&quot;: true,\r\n            &quot;autoPlay&quot;: 2000,\r\n            &quot;pauseAutoPlayOnHover&quot; : true,\r\n            &quot;prevNextButtons&quot;: true,\r\n            &quot;contain&quot; : true,\r\n            &quot;adaptiveHeight&quot; : true,\r\n            &quot;dragThreshold&quot; : 5,\r\n            &quot;percentPosition&quot;: true,\r\n            &quot;pageDots&quot;: true,\r\n            &quot;rightToLeft&quot;: false,\r\n            &quot;draggable&quot;: true,\r\n            &quot;selectedAttraction&quot;: 0.1,\r\n            &quot;parallax&quot; : 0,\r\n            &quot;friction&quot;: 0.6        }\" tabindex=\"0\">\r\n        \r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n     <div class=\"flickity-viewport\" style=\"height: 539.094px; touch-action: pan-y;\"><div class=\"flickity-slider\" style=\"left: 0px; transform: translate3d(-396.25%, 0px, 0px);\"><div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" 